      "content": "i get that, but i've been feeling like this for a few days now and i really don't want to deal with the copay or the wait at the clinic if it's nothing major. like, could i just try drinking a bunch more water and maybe taking some extra magnesium to see if it settles my stomach? i feel like dehydration is probably the real issue here.",
